### ==========================================
### Calendar API 전체 테스트
### ==========================================
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwicm9sZXMiOiJST0xFX1NUVURFTlQiLCJpYXQiOjE3Nzk5Nzc3MDksImV4cCI6MTc3OTk4MTMwOX0.n85VC_QqrRnrMAEx3RZIzDa90hYc-hz1QYilaLHlsK2ZYe63WOMdrtbovdLMxij94uSU7xAn7MeQoC4GfqBwrw

###

### ==========================================
### 정상 케이스
### ==========================================

### 1. 날짜별 캘린더 조회 - 정상
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/monthly?month=2026-05-01
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. Todo 등록 - 정상
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "모모파이터즈 화이팅",
  "start": "2026-05-27"
}

###

### 3. Todo 수정 - 정상 (2번 실행 후 calendarId 확인 후 수정)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "수정된 내용",
  "start": "2026-05-28"
}

###

### 4. Todo 체크 상태 변경 - 정상 (완료 처리)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo/1/check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isCompleted": true
}

###

### 5. Todo 체크 상태 변경 - 정상 (미완료 처리)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo/1/check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isCompleted": false
}

###

### 6. Todo 삭제 - 정상
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7. Memo 등록 - 정상 (end 있는 경우)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "생일",
  "start": "2026-05-27",
  "end": "2026-05-28"
}

###

### 8. Memo 등록 - 정상 (end 없는 경우)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "생일",
  "start": "2026-05-27"
}

###

### 9. Memo 수정 - 정상
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "수정된 메모",
  "start": "2026-05-27",
  "end": "2026-05-29"
}

###

### 10. Memo 삭제 - 정상
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ==========================================
### 400 Bad Request 케이스
### ==========================================

### 11. Todo 등록 - title 없음 (400 예상)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "start": "2026-05-27"
}

###

### 12. Todo 등록 - start 없음 (400 예상)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "모모파이터즈 화이팅"
}

###

### 13. Todo 등록 - 전체 빈값 (400 예상)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}

###

### 14. Memo 등록 - title 없음 (400 예상)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "start": "2026-05-27",
  "end": "2026-05-28"
}

###

### 15. Memo 등록 - start 없음 (400 예상)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "생일",
  "end": "2026-05-28"
}

###

### 16. Memo 등록 - end < start (400 예상)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "생일",
  "start": "2026-05-27",
  "end": "2026-05-20"
}

###

### 17. Memo 수정 - end < start (400 예상)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "수정된 메모",
  "start": "2026-05-27",
  "end": "2026-05-20"
}

###

### 18. Todo 체크 - isCompleted 없음 (400 예상)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo/1/check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}

###

### 19. 날짜 파라미터 없음 (400 예상)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/daily
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ==========================================
### 401 Unauthorized 케이스
### ==========================================

### 20. 토큰 없이 Todo 등록 (401 예상)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "모모파이터즈 화이팅",
  "start": "2026-05-27"
}

###

### 21. 토큰 없이 날짜별 조회 (401 예상)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/daily?date=2026-05-27
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 22. 잘못된 토큰 (401 예상)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer wrong_token

{
  "title": "모모파이터즈 화이팅",
  "start": "2026-05-27"
}

###

### ==========================================
### 404 Not Found 케이스
### ==========================================

### 23. 없는 Todo 수정 (404 예상)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo/9999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "수정된 내용",
  "start": "2026-05-27"
}

###

### 24. 없는 Todo 삭제 (404 예상)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 25. 없는 Todo 체크 (404 예상)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo/9999/check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isCompleted": true
}

###

### 26. 없는 Memo 수정 (404 예상)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo/9999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "수정된 메모",
  "start": "2026-05-27",
  "end": "2026-05-29"
}

###

### 27. 없는 Memo 삭제 (404 예상)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ==========================================
### 403 Forbidden 케이스
### (userId 가 다른 유저 데이터 접근 시)
### JWT 완성 후 테스트 가능
### ==========================================

### 28. 다른 유저의 Todo 수정 (403 예상)
### userId = 2L 토큰으로 userId = 1L 데이터 접근
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{other_user_token}}

{
  "title": "수정된 내용",
  "start": "2026-05-27"
}

###

### 29. 다른 유저의 Todo 삭제 (403 예상)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo/1
Authorization: Bearer {{other_user_token}}

###

### 30. 다른 유저의 Memo 수정 (403 예상)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{other_user_token}}

{
  "title": "수정된 메모",
  "start": "2026-05-27"
}

###

### 31. 다른 유저의 Memo 삭제 (403 예상)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/memo/1
Authorization: Bearer {{other_user_token}}

###

### ==========================================
### 도메인 규칙 위반 케이스
### ==========================================

### 32. Memo 에 check 요청 (400 예상)
### Memo calendarId 로 요청해야 함
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/calendar/todo/2/check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isCompleted": true
}
